{"tid":1768230,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母facebook個ps4二手group又再次俾人騎劫咗","createTime":"2019-12-04T02:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T04:36:36.000Z","uid":66260,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4607bb7ac109acfa28710e3e1667b113ccede736","tid":1768230,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T02:41:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/327925567410045/about/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F327925567410045%2Fabout%2F&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=0ae367c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/327925567410045/about/</a><br />\n變左個唔知乜撚野 無敵新聞香港 - HK Club 00<br />\n<br />\n之前試過一次, 俾班舊會員日屌夜屌先至轉返, 而家趁冇人為意又再轉過, 屌佢老母<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">做乜鳩facebook個ps4二手group比人騎戒左？？？？？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1082336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1082336</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母facebook個ps4二手group俾人騎劫咗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1079929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1079929</a><br />\n<br />\n有無fb ps4 group會員可以幫手光復PS4 group<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1079917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1079917</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班撚樣admin死性不改, 佢地今次如果再唔轉返既話<br />\n我地一齊report個page到收皮算數<br />\n一於貫徹攬炒精神</span></span>"},{"pid":"799996421c241dbbfee6491079902706b3475d08","tid":1768230,"uid":15880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T02:48:07.000Z","msg":"係咪二手佬想個group 收皮先搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e76618bc905a551319053043b36ee6481d1130c","tid":1768230,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco